%F A086302 G.f.: 8*(1 + 10*x + x^2)/(1 - x)^5. - _Colin Barker_, Mar 26 2012
%F A086302 a(n) = 4 * (n+1) * (n+2) * (n^2 + 3*n + 1). - _Bruno Berselli_, Mar 26 2012
